==English==
===Adjective===
'''sincere'''

# [[earnest]]; [[mean]]ing what one [[says]] or [[does]]; [[truthful]].
#:''I believe he is '''sincere''' in his offer to help.''
# meant [[truly]] or earnestly.
#:''She gave it a '''sincere''', if misguided effort.''

